{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0208_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0208", "six_channel": "陽明病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["陽明病"], "symptoms": ["汗出", "不惡寒", "短氣", "腹滿", "喘", "潮熱", "手足濈然汗出"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": ["遲"], "prior_treatment": [], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["大承氣湯"], "treatment_principle": ["微和胃氣"], "alternatives": ["小承氣湯"]}, "evidence_span": "陽明病，脈遲，雖汗出不惡寒者，其身必重，短氣，腹滿而喘，有潮熱者，此外欲解，可攻裏也。手足濈然汗出者，此大便已硬也，大承氣湯主之；若汗多，微發熱惡寒者，外未解也，其熱不潮，未可與承氣湯；若腹大滿不通者，可與小承氣湯，微和胃氣，勿令致大泄下。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為大承氣湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「大承氣湯主之」，證據強度：主治關係（主之）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.9, "prescription_strength": "主之", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.956, "release_level": "gold"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0209_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0209", "six_channel": "陽明病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["陽明病"], "symptoms": ["潮熱"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": [], "prior_treatment": [], "time_course": [], "contraindications": ["不可與"]}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["大承氣湯"], "treatment_principle": ["攻之", "和之"], "alternatives": ["小承氣湯", "小承氣湯"]}, "evidence_span": "陽明病，潮熱，大便微硬者，可與大承氣湯，不硬者，不可與之。若不大便六七日，恐有燥屎，欲知之法，少與小承氣湯。湯入腹中，轉矢氣者，此有燥屎也，乃可攻之；若不轉矢氣者，此但初頭硬，後必溏，不可攻之，攻之必脹滿不能食也。欲飲水者，與水則噦。其後發熱者，必大便復硬而少也，以小承氣湯和之。不轉矢氣者，慎不可攻也。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為大承氣湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「大承氣湯」，證據強度：斟酌可用（可與）。本條同時載明禁忌「不可與」，用方須以該禁忌為前提。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.82, "prescription_strength": "可與", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "warn", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": ["repair:contraindication_annotated:不可與"], "consensus_score": 0.813, "release_level": "silver"}}
